      <h3>Quick Answer</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>The anabolic window is not 30 minutes — it's closer to 2 hours, and it matters less than total intake</li>
        <li>The #1 timing lever: get 30g of protein at breakfast — most men miss this entirely</li>
        <li>Spread protein across 3–4 meals instead of loading it at dinner</li>
        <li>Before bed is the most underused timing window — cottage cheese works well here</li>
        <li>You don't need to eat every 2 hours — that's unnecessary and exhausting</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

